846ef3aa09a2840d52e20a4b2276ec9dd68b972","tid":1606800,"uid":52621,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b9357d8bc4f9f39f01af0eae72ad658bf01183f","tid":1606800,"uid":181998,"like":26,"dislike":7,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:03:58.000Z","msg":"聽日空城計 可以浪費敵方兵力 又不做成傷亡 但會失去左一次進攻機會 而且呢刻先決定唔出去 會賣左一班手足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:38:09.000Z","msg":"敵進我退<br />\n我認為聽日 和平行最好 因為大把外媒<br />\n黑警一定忍唔到 各大頭條&quot;黑警血腥鎮壓和平遊行&quot; 香港人道危機更明顯<br />\n10.1之後有D外媒會走 再打好過 10.1拎暴力場面本錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51dfb5fd85b152fc76fb9a0b5a940be97c917189","tid":1606800,"uid":290973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:38:42.000Z","msg":"屌完冇畀建議？<br />\nBtw 樓主小米機未爆炸？"},{"pid":"32f8bd0a9750aa29ee380077dc6d175f7631eb8f","tid":1606800,"uid":101439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:39:18.000Z","msg":"不推文回覆"},{"pid":"ed3d422e4d591f1be249a7f55718aebc907d1f6d","tid":1606800,"uid":136249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"179e43b9ff068769afd72a01c37bb00162a3b520","tid":1606800,"uid":271016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:32:05.000Z","msg":"次次見到打黎做乜撚都好想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n閣下認為應該幾時打?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:39:30.000Z","msg":"其實唔係打經濟戰仲好咩.. 放料話遊行 d鋪都已經唔開.. 加埋間唔中發起window shopping<br />\n如果持之以恆 肯定有用 手足又唔會俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知咁講會俾人屌 但真係好擔心聽日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31845afdc04aa039a5bf294a7c3010107faf6050","tid":1606800,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n樓主三毛帶風向 準備死全家啦屌你老母閪"},{"pid":"c644fb67ee942f7cd634860d5d850e97f7810958","tid":1606800,"uid":185022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:39:56.000Z","msg":"大家唔洗理佢<br />